result.formatted_address: 3/F, Somptueux Central, 52 Wellington St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: HONI HONI Tiki Cocktail Lounge

reviews.text: A very cool bar with a nice deal for happy hour. The service is awesome. Location is perfect. Would definitely come back again.
Worth a go at happy hour or if you're happier to pay more than the neighbours.  :) nice atmosphere,  service and drinks.  All carefully designed and served.
Since years a great place in the heart of Hong Kong with roof top terrace. Great place serving nice cocktails. Perfect to let some stress go
Cocktails were good, but pricey. Atmosphere was fine. Didn't like it when they opened the doors and smoke from fellow customers on the balcony blew inside.

Awesome bar and service! Friendly staff too! It felt great to be treated nicely especially in this rude HK society generally.

I had Matomato, such a refreshing drink that served in unique (and cultural i guess?) glass, to quench my thirst in the humid hot summer.
